column5: Went to a farm to get eggs today. Saw this sign: "I dream of a world where chickens can cross the road without having their motives questioned."
LOL. Poor chickens living in a judgmental society.
I saw a sign at the end of a laneway one day and it read..... Rabbits 4 Sale Meat or Pet You Choose
Why didn't the skeleton cross the road?  . . . . . . . . . . . . because he didn't have the guts to.
why did the chicken cross the road?  to show the skunk that you can
